### A. BACKEND — Repository Pattern + Thin Controller

#### [NEW] [BaseRepository.js](file:///d:/Carzy/packages/api/src/repositories/base/BaseRepository.js)
Class cha trừu tượng: `findById`, `findOne`, `find`, [create](file:///d:/Carzy/packages/api/src/services/userService.js#5-13), `updateById`, `deleteById`, `paginate`.

#### [NEW] [VehicleRepository.js](file:///d:/Carzy/packages/api/src/repositories/VehicleRepository.js)
Kế thừa BaseRepository. Chứa mọi Mongoose query liên quan Vehicle:
- `findAllWithPagination(filters, pagination)` — thay cho query trong getAllVehicles
- `findByIdWithUser(id)` — thay cho Vehicle.findById().populate()
- `findByUser(userId)` — thay cho Vehicle.find({user})
- `findForAdmin(filters, pagination)` — thay cho getVehiclesForAdmin query
- `quickSearch(query)` — full-text search

#### [NEW] [UserRepository.js](file:///d:/Carzy/packages/api/src/repositories/UserRepository.js)
Kế thừa BaseRepository. Chứa mọi Mongoose query liên quan User:
- `findByEmail(email)`
- `findWithStats(userId)` — user + vehicleCount + favoriteCount

